9581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:34:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"419f497ca95380b7d3c4c183991f446a7bb7cd60","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:44:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ea808d9466de4e7793425cd20c16e27ec7b7bef","tid":1379581,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e909263cc08c736af024a85e96ab3e493b16076c","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:03:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>（睇晒先評，下面有建議）</strong><br />\n五大訴求大家應該堅持，但「第四訴求」&mdash;&mdash;「獨立調查黑警」又係咪應該用「調查委員會」方式進行？你睇下以往既獨立調查，大概就會估到結果：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">九巴19死車禍意外調查委員會</span></strong><br />\n以調查為由不公開整份中期報告，提出45項建議<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">沙中線工程調查委員會</span></strong><br />\n以調查為由不公開整份中期報告，並指工程達到安全水平<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">南丫島撞船事故調查委員會</span></strong></strong><br />\n以調查為由不公佈整份報告，尤其涉事船長調查報告<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">食水含鉛超標調查委員會</span></strong><br />\n集體失職，無個人具體負上任何民事及刑事責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>大家可以預計「黑警獨立調查委員」會出現乜野結果，最大可能就係&mdash;&mdash;調查報告不公開，最終回到「警察查警察」既局面，同你去警投訴科有乜分別？</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n通常調查都要一年甚至幾年，結果香港人就因為覺得「已經有獨立調查」，公義就已經彰顯，所謂中間派就會收晒貨，然後問你做乜仲示威，大家要有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家要相對有效地<strong><ins>「獨立調查黑警」</ins></strong>，獨立調查就<strong><ins>唔應該用委員會方式</ins></strong>進行，有網友提出左一個方案：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>係成立類似證監會既監警機構，立一條新法賦權畀新機構調查</strong>，以《打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集條例》為例，<strong><ins>調查權力非常大，銷毀証據會犯刑事，甚至可以命令當事人畀口供，即係冇緘默權，甚至畀假口供都係犯刑事，不過就唔係可當作刑事証據，只可以作「紀律處分」</ins></strong>。同埋立一條新法，我當保皇黨都支持，我估快極都半年，到時又會「畀時間黑警毀滅證據」。<br />\n<br />\n（我聽過有人提到交畀廉署查，但根據《廉政公署條例》廉署既逮捕權係不涉及暴力罪行）<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？  <br />\n參考自網友：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rabbitobaggio/posts/10157958661445769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frabbitobaggio%2Fposts%2F10157958661445769&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=fc109a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rabbitobaggio/posts/10157958661445769</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"贊同<br />\n<br />\n齋成立獨立調查委員會係冇用<br />\n只不過今次一定牽涉中共，我唔認為會查到啲乜嘢出嚟<br />\n總之就係廢，除非係獨立後嘅政府查"},{"pid":"0cce440cf654f3f13b5d7e42a82974e7ab7f67c0","tid":1379581,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:59:25.000Z","msg":"無普選立法會，乜撚調查都可以無作用，無賴獨裁政權做乜都得"},{"pid":"1125fa1b30919f346965e703c6c84e1e4a1c51f9","tid":1379581,"uid":265783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c88d636281fbac4ecb1d9a539b17c51ea1c78df","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"聽完國務院記招就知爭拗「普選」定「獨立調查委員會」重要，或者畀更多建議去加強獨立調查效果，都係無乜意思，中國政府已明確撐警，中國治下唔會畀你查黑警。"},{"pid":"652a89e6187669230abbfe3537c6d77f994f4b20","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287a5aa1fa3ee2ddc7054a535215f079b86c57be","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c61b4b1c0471449129edf32194696aae38a326","tid":1379581,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"82fe5e754c06f9fc31d33bb71a153e6980594fc5","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d616aed3e6d0a025a4c03c921b855cd658b8901","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986d4d5c391bd207376c06fdfd4846ed9ee6186e","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"91e2190a19d6c8b2f1bc6b4b1e3008d7b206f015","tid":1379581,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"adb7a9d37f859ceebc781166ba1c54d56885cf3d","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"366a370b5f6d6ce06717f641d0a4d864998cf6cf","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07344fd7b93f4c8da99ea372a6dd1cea2966c128","tid":1379581,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"}]}